00:29:33,236 --> 00:29:35,246
Thank you, Honey.

436
00:29:36,116 --> 00:29:38,676
Dad, thank you so much. I love you.

437
00:29:38,676 --> 00:29:43,076
Ma Ri looks happier that you're starting a production company.

438
00:29:43,076 --> 00:29:45,106
Are you that happy?

439
00:29:45,106 --> 00:29:48,876
You were saying you hated her just a few days ago.

440
00:29:49,596 --> 00:29:51,426
The two of you...

