00:29:58,486 --> 00:30:02,376
What did you say? Cutting water with a knife?

444
00:30:06,706 --> 00:30:09,446
Where did you learn that phrase?

445
00:30:13,636 --> 00:30:16,736
Ji Yeong, here.

446
00:30:17,796 --> 00:30:22,396
President Lee, I'm nervous to death right now.

447
00:30:22,396 --> 00:30:25,146
My heart is about to pop out.

448
00:30:25,146 --> 00:30:27,776
I can't think of any lines, either.

449
00:30:27,776 --> 00:30:31,216
My head hurts, and I think I'll throw up.

450
00:30:31,216 --> 00:30:34,486
What? I-If so...

451
00:30:34,486 --> 00:30:38,616
I'll go get you chungshimhwan*. Wait just a moment. 
  (T/N: Calming herbal medicine) 

452
00:30:46,726 --> 00:30:49,786
What do I do? We're about to start filming soon.

