00:30:50,506 --> 00:30:52,946
Why am I so nervous?

454
00:31:06,386 --> 00:31:07,786
Director.

455
00:31:07,786 --> 00:31:11,186
 Ji Yeong, you must be nervous since it's your first shoot. 

