00:31:15,946 --> 00:31:17,256
Are you okay?

459
00:31:17,256 --> 00:31:19,966
Yes, I-I'm...

460
00:31:19,966 --> 00:31:22,166
I-I'm okay.

461
00:31:22,166 --> 00:31:24,886
I'd get even more nervous if you were around.

