00:32:21,726 --> 00:32:24,766
"Baby chick"? What baby chick?

481
00:32:26,336 --> 00:32:29,876
There are a lot of people around me right now.

482
00:32:29,876 --> 00:32:34,926
If I say, "baby chick," from now on, it means I like you.

483
00:32:34,926 --> 00:32:36,876
What did you say?

484
00:32:42,496 --> 00:32:44,316
Okay.

485
00:32:46,056 --> 00:32:47,876
Chirp, chirp.

486
00:32:49,786 --> 00:32:52,946
- Baby chick. 
 - Chirp, chirp.

