00:33:47,026 --> 00:33:48,616
Was I okay?

497
00:33:48,616 --> 00:33:51,056
Are you kidding me?

498
00:33:51,056 --> 00:33:53,136
Ji Yeong, you did a great job.

499
00:33:53,136 --> 00:33:56,716
Why is Jae Dong next to that country bumpkin?

