00:33:56,716 --> 00:33:58,916
Jae Dong! Hey!

501
00:33:58,916 --> 00:34:02,266
Why are you with that country bumpkin?

502
00:34:02,266 --> 00:34:05,786
President Baek, I started an entertainment company.

503
00:34:07,186 --> 00:34:09,886
And she's not a country bumpkin. She's Kim Ji Yeong.

504
00:34:09,886 --> 00:34:11,796
She's my first actor.

505
00:34:11,796 --> 00:34:16,896
Popcorn Entertainment? So... she's an actor at your company?

